subSection.paragraph:
Multiple sequence alignments were performed in Clustal X 2.0.12 with default parameters (
Thompson et al . 1997
). All sequences were edited and translated into amino acids in MEGA 7.0.26 (
Kumar et al . 2016
). The software MEGA 7.0.26 (
Kumar et al . 2016
) was also used to calculate the Kimura-2-Parameter distance and reconstruct a neighbor-joining (NJ) tree. Node support values were estimated with 1000 bootstrap replicates.

